This set of runs is not intended to be realistic; the data values are just
numerical values to test the validity of the interfaces between the classes
and the external models.

RUN_0*  These runs cover the various nominal run options
RUN_1*  These runs cover non-terminal mis-configurations
RUN_2*  These runs cover terminal errors.

Verification Status:
Have checked that:
- tables are getting loaded appropriately
- model is capable of using appropriate environment variables to extract values
  from the tables for the various coefficients.
- usage is configurable at the input file level.
- dispersions can be specified and applied appropriately.
- appropriate protections are in place to prevent conflicting demands.

Have not checked:
- The computations of derived coefficients, e.g. CD, CS, CL from CX, CY, CZ.
